Update 243

What follows are the changes visible in the data files for update 243.

THIS SECTION IS IN BETA! Not all changes are detected yet.

Additions

New skills

SKILLDescription
Buckle ArtistrySkill in creating belt buckles with symbolic meanings. Belt buckle artwork is a deeply personal expression which can give hammer warriors a morale boost in battle. However, because they are so personal, crafted belt buckles are only useful to the person who crafts them.

New powers

New items

New recipes
